{"tid":2159422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"照顧確診者 醫護不獲N95","createTime":"2020-08-16T10:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T11:07:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc4f3dc0c2c4b53eee20629819d89b252433194","tid":2159422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/4BEXG5RA5RHPBD2DLF7TGMJHYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2F4BEXG5RA5RHPBD2DLF7TGMJHYM%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=0794c1d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2F4BEXG5RA5RHPBD2DLF7TGMJHYM%2F&h=e2f9e3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/4BEXG5RA5RHPBD2DLF7TGMJHYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n照顧確診者 醫護不獲N95<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kQHmTAx6_RzC8gegC4Yih0IOxqk=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MEHIIZKZWNACLEKUXER7SNXHSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkQHmTAx6_RzC8gegC4Yih0IOxqk%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMEHIIZKZWNACLEKUXER7SNXHSI.jpg&h=375dd655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有調查顯示，逾半受訪前線醫護認為醫院裝備不足、人手短缺。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港醫療人員總工會的調查顯示，逾半前線醫護人員不滿個人防護裝備不足及人手緊絀，其中有抽血員需進入隔離病房，院方卻指「只是入去抽幾個血」，拒絕發給防護較高的N95口罩。<br />\n<br />\n調查在7月21日至8月5日透過網上問卷訪問了826名前線醫護人員，當中五成四受訪者認為裝備不足夠，有五成一人稱因抽調。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各病房至少欠四員工<br />\n<br />\n醫管局支援職系員工協會理事長吳偉玲指出，目前內科、外科、骨科等病房，每個病房至少有兩名護士、兩名支援職系員工被抽調到隔離病房，令每個病房至少缺四名員工，希望醫管局可以重新聘請已退休前員工，紓緩人手不足。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理庾慧玲表示，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6535bc13e557bbc1eed08d29d3b76e77a776c69b","tid":2159422,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"DKLM"},{"pid":"520e7771cf7f1238bd6ac844f39c7d771961c012","tid":2159422,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母HA"},{"pid":"908c49d12a40fa31567c30c29ea36248cafd98c5","tid":2159422,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"黑警 全套"},{"pid":"966406feed330ed4076a4c42c749bc214edc7c96","tid":2159422,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"908c49d12a40fa31567c30c29ea36248cafd98c5","tid":2159422,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"黑警 全套"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">黑警死全家，準備有報應</span>"},{"pid":"5c6fc4d95ffe90d9e99167bbc3d30c6dcedc2c7e","tid":2159422,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"哈 岩岩tvb仲話ha有充足物資，夠用四個月"},{"pid":"af3c2d7aa8c64ef882530309ed073dc49af4a2a5","tid":2159422,"uid":101193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"而家跟本就當醫護係condom 完左武肺就開始清算"}]}